channel.title: Starting up (REP++) (PI)
channel.description:
Every time I run my Webclient it just says 'Starting up', and does nothing...
It cache downloads properly, because on my jarred version (one on my desktop) it works fine and so does the Client.
So what could be the error!? I'm using 000webhost, to host.
